creator: FCM Travel Solutions
descriptionHtml:
This is FCM’s brand new app for 2022. The app has been designed to be the mobile companion to the desktop version of FCM’s new ‘FCM Platform’ travel management tool. The app is best used for those clients and customers who have recently launched, or migrated to ‘FCM Platform’.

This is the mobile channel for FCM Platform, FCM Travel’s omnichannel digital experience for business travel customers. This app is best used by customers who have recently migrated onto the new FCM Platform for itinerary management and online travel booking.

**This is a beta version, and minor bugs are expected. We are actively working on improving the app.

**Some features might differ slightly in web and app due to mobile format and user experience.

- Access your automatically synched itinerary, any time and anywhere. And if you are booking additional trips, we have you covered with the manual trip forms.
- Access your travel itinerary anywhere, from any device. Trips booked through FCM Travel will be automatically synchronised to your itinerary. Booked a component on your own? No problem, you can also manually add segments and organise them into trips.
- Receive notifications from Sam on the status of your trip: gate changes, flight delays, check-in reminders, etc.
- Get notified for key information and alerts for your trip; from check-in reminders and gate information to flight delays and safety alerts.
- Get in touch with a travel consultant, via chat or phone
- Keep in touch while on the go with company communications and interactive chat with your travel consultant.
- Stay informed with security alerts, powered by WorldAware. Critical alerts include information like emergency numbers, both local and from your security provider.

This app is only available to FCM Travel customers.
descriptionShort: Wherever you are, FCM travel Platform will help you keep your trip hassle-free

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
What’s new?
- Conferma Pay app integration for those customers who use it to pre-authorise payment for hotel bookings. Conferma is a virtual payment method, generally used to book hotels. Rather than the traveller needing a physical credit card, a secure, single-use virtual card is generated to use as the form of payment.
- Several fixes and improvements

creator: FCM Travel Solutions
descriptionHtml:
Manage Your Trip with Ease

- Instant Itinerary Access: View your travel plans anytime, anywhere, from any device. Booked through FCM Travel? Your trips sync automatically. Adding trips yourself? No problem—you can manually add and organize them.
- Real-Time Travel Alerts: Get essential notifications like check-in reminders, gate updates, delays, and safety alerts to keep you informed every step of the way.
- Stay Connected with Your Travel Consultant: Need support? Reach out via chat or phone to get in touch with a consultant whenever you need help.
- Security Alerts: Stay safe with real-time security notifications, including local emergency contacts and provider support in critical situations.

Note: This app is exclusively for FCM Travel customers.
